In this update we are introducing LYK Business Pages. This includes: Creating a business page Editing a business page info Creating business posts Creating business promotions Users can follow business pages In addition to this there have been a few bug fixes and performance improvements.

In this update we have made improvements to our Posting feature. This includes improvements on: Creating a post Uploading pictures videos and location Sharing post with specific audience Going live Posting Event Cropping pictures Posting text and emojis In addition to this there have been a few bug fixes and performance improvements.

In this update we have made improvements to the profile and activity screens. This includes improvements on: Adding your own display picture Updating your own profile information Viewing your own profile screen Viewing another user s profile screen Sending connection request through another user s profile screen Changing connection status with another user through another user s profile screen Creating chats through another user s profile screen Blocking another user through their profile screen In addition to this there have been a few bug fixes and performance improvements.
